---

<section class="whoami-page">
  <div class="bg-sky"></div>
  <div class="bg-grass"></div>

  <div class="decorations">
    <span class="deco" style="top: 10%; left: 5%;">🌸</span>
    <span class="deco" style="top: 20%; right: 10%;">🌼</span>
    <span class="deco" style="bottom: 25%; left: 8%;">🍀</span>
    <span class="deco" style="bottom: 18%; right: 5%;">🌻</span>
  </div>

  <div class="wood-frame">
    <div class="parchment">
      <h1 class="title">🌻 我是谁</h1>

      <div class="columns">
        <div class="intro-col">
          <p class="intro-text">
            港大市场营销硕士，擅长数据驱动增长与 AI 产品运营
          </p>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p class="intro-desc">
            相信好的产品力 + 运营力 + 数据力，能够创造可持续的增长飞轮。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bubble-col">
          <div class="bubble-group">
            <span class="group-label">🏢 实习经历</span>
            <div class="bubble-row">
              <div class="bubble company lg">字节跳动</div>
              <div class="bubble company md">小红书</div>
              <div class="bubble company md">美团</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bubble-row">
              <div class="bubble company sm">哈啰</div>
              <div class="bubble company sm">美敦力</div>
              <div class="bubble company sm">默克</div>
              <div class="bubble company sm">安永</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble-group">
            <span class="group-label">📜 证书</span>
            <div class="bubble-row">
              <div class="bubble cert">港大硕士</div>
              <div class="bubble cert">IELTS 7.5</div>
              <div class="bubble cert">ACCA</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble-group">
            <span class="group-label">💼 能力</span>
            <div class="bubble-row">
              <div class="bubble skill">数据分析</div>
              <div class="bubble skill">电商运营</div>
              <div class="bubble skill">AI产品</div>
              <div class="bubble skill">大促策略</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble-group">
            <span class="group-label">🎵 爱好</span>
            <div class="bubble-row">
              <div class="bubble hobby">🎤 唱歌</div>
              <div class="bubble hobby">🎧 听音乐</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .whoami-page {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bg-sky {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 65%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #87CEEB 0%, #B4E7CE 100%);
  }

  .bg-grass {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 40%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #7CB342 0%, #558B2F 100%);
  }

  .decorations {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .deco {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 2rem;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }

  .wood-frame {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #A0522D 50%, #6B3E26 100%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .parchment {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F5E6C8 0%, #E8DCC8 100%);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 36px;
    max-width: 780px;
    max-height: 88vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .title {
    font-family: 'ZCOOL QingKe HuangYou', cursive;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #5D3A1A;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 650px) {
    .columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .intro-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #5D3A1A;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 50px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #8B4513;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }

  .intro-desc {
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #6B5344;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .bubble-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .bubble-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .group-label {
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #8B4513;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .bubble-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .bubble {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .bubble:hover {
    transform: scale(1.08) translateY(-2px);
  }

  .company {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #64B5F6, #42A5F5);
  }

  .company.lg { width: 85px; height: 85px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .company.md { width: 70px; height: 70px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .company.sm { width: 58px; height: 58px; font-size: 0.7rem; }

  .cert {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #FFC107);
    color: #5D3A1A;
    width: 65px;
    height: 65px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .skill {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #81C784, #66BB6A);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .hobby {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F48FB1, #F06292);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .nav-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 20px;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .wood-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8B4513 0%, #6B3E26 100%);
    color: #FDF5E6;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'ZCOOL QingKe HuangYou', cursive;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 0 #5D3A1A, 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .wood-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #A0522D 0%, #8B4513 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #5D3A1A, 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .wood-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(1px);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #5D3A1A, 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }
</style>